次 都係佢地四圍爬先搵到<br />\n根本無呢埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家懷疑緊係 空隙位 訓緊教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca8e7d94053acbdb3a2929aed84a435ee180df5","tid":388453,"uid":65083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我走失過兩次 都係佢地四圍爬先搵到<br />\n根本無呢埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家懷疑緊係 空隙位 訓緊教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n餓多幾日會出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsofa底, 雪櫃, 廁所都有發現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2e75a26b37a207af793bf733d73984752fe4b0","tid":388453,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"變左神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食晒d曱甴"},{"pid":"42b8e83e791b595a6aef807bc0d7eb866c867c35","tid":388453,"uid":69098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"我果隻走過入梳化底<br />\n搵到我傻，好彩唔係去咗電視櫃後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55bdb4e8267f81b3aa0fabfc4a9e51d042a9eb5","tid":388453,"uid":51201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果隻走過入梳化底<br />\n搵到我傻，好彩唔係去咗電視櫃後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我電視機底 黑到照都照唔到 又多塵  <br />\n最怕佢舔左啲有毒性野 如漂白水 洗潔精 甲甴筆  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029091f31b9ef0daa5017fe510293eaad8255216","tid":388453,"uid":134130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}